## Notes

- The map implementation is solid and well-structured. The polygon-based SVG approach is flexible and renders efficiently.
- All 8 ranches with `fieldLotToSection` mappings now have corresponding `vineyardSections` entries with SVG polygons.
- XSS protection via `_esc()` is correctly applied to user-derived lot names in the detail table.
- `cleanupLabSamples` has proper `try/finally` for `_uploading` flag.
- The `_renderRanchTabs` optimization (skip rebuild when count matches) is a good touch.
- Upload pipeline cleanup expanded to cover EXPERIMENT/EXPERIMENTO patterns, NORMAL exact match, CONFIG `_excludedSamples`, and California appellation — comprehensive.
- Screenshots saved: `test-results/map-desktop.png`, `test-results/map-mobile.png`
- No Priority 1 issues. 5 minor P2 improvements remain. Code is ready for deployment.
